but I heard today there are hundreds of thousands of refugees trekking east.
今天就有几十万灾民东迁

208
00:10:57,960 --> 00:11:00,730
Did you know Nevada is one of the most  populous states in the Union now?
知道现在内华达州是全美人口最多的州吗？

209
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:05,710
