222
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,500
But supplies of that are getting very thin.
但这种药已经供不上了

223
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:43,400
And I heard the head pharmacist say we might be completely out by the end of the month.
我听药房说最多坚持到月底

224
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,340
That sucks.
太倒霉了

225
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:47,100
Yeah. Yeah.
是啊 是啊

226
00:11:47,970 --> 00:11:51,030
Yeah, that sucks. It, it really sucks.
是的 太倒霉了 真的太倒霉了

227
