互联网瘫痪 加州下沉

228
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:58,650
There's fires and famines and plagues and all the rest.
还有大火 饥荒 疫情和各种灾难

229
00:11:58,670 --> 00:12:02,490
I mean, it just the center doesn't hold.
连我们医院也快崩溃了

230
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:06,380
It just won't let up.
有完没完

231
00:12:08,210 --> 00:12:11,020
How long is this gonna go on?
那天还有多久？

232
00:12:11,730 --> 00:12:14,410
How much can we take before the whole thing...
那之前还能撑多久？

233
00:12:14,690 --> 00:12:17,660
before the whole thing goes apart, I mean.
我是说 天塌下来前

