你听说过他的宇宙历年法吗？

237
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:33,080
Uh... I don't know. I don't think so.
呃 想不起来 应该没听过

238
00:12:33,100 --> 00:12:36,340
Well, the universe is 15 billion years old.
你知道 宇宙已有150亿年历史

239
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:41,240
And if you took all of that all, all 15 billion years
如果你把这150亿年

240
00:12:41,330 --> 00:12:45,400
and compress them into a single calendar year,
都给它压缩到365天的日历中

241
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:49,250
then the Big Bang happens in the first second, January 1st.
那么宇宙大爆炸发生在1月1日第一秒

242
00:12:45,490 --> 00:12:49,040
{\an8}一月份

243
00:12:49,225 --> 00:12:51,575
And, and today,
而如今

244
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:58,820
oh, right now, we're in the final millisecond of the last minute of the last day, December 31st.
我们正处于12月31日 最后一天的最后一刻

245
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,440
{\an8}十二月份

246
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,760
But if you go back to the start,
回到起点

247
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:06,110
if the, if the Big Bang happens at midnight, January 1st,
回到大爆炸发生的1月1日夜里

248
00:13:06,130 --> 00:13:10,200
then each month of this calendar is one and a quarter billion years long.
日历里每个月等于12.5亿年

249
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:12,480
Hey, nobody told me there was math on this exam.
嘿 别考我数学

250
00:13:12,530 --> 00:13:15,210
The universe starts January 1st,
宇宙在1月1日诞生

251
00:13:15,230 --> 00:13:19,900
but the, uh, the Milky Way didn't form until May.
但此时我们的银河系还没形成 形成要到5月

252
00:13:18,230 --> 00:13:19,540
{\an8}五月份

253
00:13:19,930 --> 00:13:25,440
Our sun and our earth, they don't show up until mid-September.
我们的太阳和地球 要到9月中旬才形成

254
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,010
{\an8}九月份

255
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:28,440
Life appears soon after. But not us.
生命不久后就有了 但没轮到我们

256
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:31,570
No. No, no, we don't appear for guess how long?
猜猜我们什么时候出现的？

257
00:13:31,590 --> 00:13:33,790
Again, I was told there'd be no math.
再说一遍 今天不考数学

258
00:13:33,810 --> 00:13:36,080
December 31st.
在12月31日

259
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,690
Last day on the calendar,
出现在日历上的最后一天

260
00:13:35,898 --> 00:13:37,750
{\an8}十二月份

261
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:44,310
and the very first human beings on Earth made their debut around 10:30 p.m.
最早的人类出现在晚上10点半左右

262
00:13:44,350 --> 00:13:47,810
10:30 p.m. on the last day.
出现在最后一天的晚上10点半

263
00:13:47,830 --> 00:13:52,200
And, um, every minute since then is 30,000 years.
每一分钟代表着3万年

264
00:13:52,220 --> 00:14:01,860
So, 11:46 p.m., only 14 minutes ago, humanity tamed fire
晚上11:46 距离午夜14分钟 人类才学会用火

265
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:05,790
and now we're out of minutes, we're into seconds.
在距离午夜只剩几秒钟时

266
00:14:05,930 --> 00:14:07,830
11:59 and 20 seconds,
到11点59分20秒

267
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:15,920
the domestication of plants and animals begin, an application for the human talent for making tools.
动植物才被驯化 人类刚开始能制造工具

268
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:19,270
11:59 and 35 seconds,
到11点59分35秒

269
00:14:19,290 --> 00:14:25,060
agricultural communities evolved into the first cities.
农耕社区演变为首批城市雏形

