01:23:20,430 --> 01:23:25,100
I wonder if maybe next semester you might want to try Math League after school.
我觉得你下学期课后应该报个数学竞赛社

1130
01:23:25,130 --> 01:23:29,040
I did it all high school, in fact, and it was so great.
我整个高中都在参加 特有趣

1131
01:23:29,060 --> 01:23:32,070
I'm doing Twirlers and Spinners.
我现在报的是舞蹈社团

1132
01:23:32,220 --> 01:23:33,820
Yeah.
对

1133
01:23:35,150 --> 01:23:38,630
Hey, hey, put that down for a second, will you?
嘿 先放下笔 先听我说说

1134
01:23:38,660 --> 01:23:41,090
Just a little about math.
说点数学的事

1135
01:23:41,120 --> 01:23:44,390
Because people start out thinking it might be boring,
人们最初都以为它很枯燥

1136
01:23:44,410 --> 01:23:46,960
and that's their first mistake.
这就是错在起点

1137
01:23:46,980 --> 01:23:50,410
It's used in every career, in every job,
无论干什么职业 做哪份工作

1138
01:23:50,440 --> 01:23:53,480
in every facet of life on this planet.
地球上生活的方方面面都离不开它

1139
01:23:53,500 --> 01:23:56,700
That's a fact. Hell, the planet.
毋庸置疑 就连地球自己也离不开它

1140
01:23:56,730 --> 01:23:59,800
