又怎么建桥 盖楼 测星距

1149
01:24:28,020 --> 01:24:29,830
How did we land on the moon?
怎么登月的？

1150
01:24:29,850 --> 01:24:34,680
The stars themselves. Why they burn, why atoms split and fuse,
星星是怎么燃烧的？原子怎么聚变裂变的？

1151
01:24:34,710 --> 01:24:37,840
and all the rest is just math.
这些都离不开数学

1152
01:24:37,860 --> 01:24:40,580
Hey, stars are just math.
星星本身就是数学产物

1153
01:24:40,610 --> 01:24:42,540
When you look at the night sky,
当你仰望夜空时

1154
01:24:42,560 --> 01:24:46,630
you're seeing the greatest equation in the universe.
看到的是宇宙最壮丽的方程式

1155
01:24:46,650 --> 01:24:49,460
