舞蹈的语言到底是什么？

1157
01:24:52,480 --> 01:24:54,450
How do you learn your steps?
你怎么学舞步的？

1158
01:24:54,480 --> 01:24:58,040
 It's even in the name. I mean, they call it "the count."
名字就在那里 叫数拍

1159
01:24:58,070 --> 01:24:59,680
