一 二 三 四

1160
01:24:59,700 --> 01:25:02,510
What's a waltz? One, two, three, one, two, three.
华尔兹呢？一 二 三 一 二 三

1161
01:25:02,530 --> 01:25:05,690
Just numbers, just math.
全是数字 都是数学

1162
01:25:05,710 --> 01:25:07,800
And more than that,
不仅如此

1163
01:25:07,830 --> 01:25:10,610
there's an art to it.
数学可以是门艺术

1164
01:25:10,630 --> 01:25:15,570
What I do, all these files here, all these folders,
我干的活儿 你看这堆文件 这些档案

1165
01:25:15,590 --> 01:25:18,320
these are all people's lives.
记录的都是人们的生活

1166
01:25:18,350 --> 01:25:20,970
Every choice they made.
他们每个选择

1167
01:25:20,990 --> 01:25:23,390
Last year, last 10 years.
去年 过去十年

1168
01:25:23,410 --> 01:25:25,540
Everything that's important to them.
他们在意的一切

1169
01:25:25,560 --> 01:25:28,710
Every weakness they have, every vice, every dream,
所有缺点 嗜好和梦想

1170
01:25:28,730 --> 01:25:32,670
it's all here in numbers.
全都体现在数字里

1171
01:25:32,690 --> 01:25:35,150
